INFLUENCE THE REPRESENTATION OF HELIX 6 AND STRAND 3 OF
SHEET *S1*.  THE PAPER CITED AS REFERENCE 26 ABOVE SHOULD
BE CONSULTED FOR THESE SUBTLETIES.
;
